<td id="4D625DE3FF85004CFE64BCD1FCA8FEA2" box="[434,894,232,293]" gridcol="1" gridrow="1" pageId="2" pageNumber="99">With white stripe on the fore margin at base, Cub vein reaching to the apex of tegmen</td>
